2.00	Balance_of_Power_(Red_Dwarf)	Balance of Power (Red Dwarf)	"Balance of Power" is the third episode of science fiction comedy Red Dwarf series one. It was first broadcast on the British television channel BBC2 on 29 February 1988. Written by Rob Grant and Doug Naylor, and directed by Ed Bye. The story revolves around Lister's desire to bring his one true love, Kristine Kochanski, back as a hologram.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/d/d4/RD_Balance_of_Power.jpg/250px-RD_Balance_of_Power.jpg
